data.description: Welcome to your new home in Locust Grove, GA—a cozy retreat that combines practicality with comfort. This charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom traditional-style house is waiting to welcome you with open arms.  Step through the inviting 2-story foyer and into a space designed for both relaxation and functionality. The formal dining room and versatile office/playroom offer flexible living options to suit your lifestyle.  In the kitchen, new appliances and a pantry make meal prep a breeze, while the adjacent breakfast nook is perfect for casual dining. With a 2-car garage and fenced yard, this home provides the convenience and security you desire.  Enjoy the ease of maintenance with tile and wood floors throughout, along with the peace of mind of a new roof. Located in a subdivision without HOA fees, you have the freedom to make this house your own without any extra hassle.  Explore the nearby attractions, shops, and dining options, or take a short drive to Atlanta for even more excitement. Whether you're starting your journey as a homeowner or looking for a cozy place to call your own, this affordably priced house is ready to become your perfect haven. Don't miss out—schedule a showing today!
